com.paypal.selion.platform.dataprovider.filter

Interface DataProviderFilter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CustomKeyFilter, SimpleIndexInclusionFilter

    public interface DataProviderFilter
    This Interface provides the facility to provide the custom filtering logic based on the needs. user can create the custom filter class by implementing this filter and invoke the filter based methods to apply the filter.

    Example dataproviderfilter: 
     public class SimpleIndexInclusionDataProviderFilter implements IDataProviderFilter {
 
     @Override
     public Object[][] filter(Object[][] data, String... args) {
         // filtering logic here
         return filteredData;
     }
 
 }
